咁多位香港人有國際級嘅能力勝任職位先至有㗎<br />\n香港啲筍工係屬於你㗎<br />\n<br />\n現實嘅香港人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁鍾意錢嘅香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">成日要返工不了嘅香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家港共政府搶你錢，搶你工，搶你嘅經濟繁榮呀</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲等？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:37:50.000Z","msg":"和平理性非暴力已經唔再有用<br />\n試咗咁多次，政府都係當食花生咁笑鳩我地<br />\n係咪應該用啲激進嘅手段呢？<br />\n你不仁我不義<br />\n香港人而家最需要就係團結，理想d講就係要推翻政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜香港大部分人仲係抱住聽日返工不了嘅心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港豬就全部係到飲喜茶，睇吳亦凡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237931710d66dc300b778cdc6a92f7d79d39bf8b","tid":858194,"uid":126529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fff0efb3a80cca585a28a9d7518e051a5741789c","tid":858194,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T03:06:28.000Z","msg":"🤷🏻&zwj;♂️大家有沒唸過爛尾，普通市民都一定唔好受"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:39:24.000Z","msg":"五毛識打字未 <br />\n諗<br />\n爛乜撚尾 仲有野好輸咩"},{"pid":"d1f1e9c8a73344ef0415781222573919d7991f4b","tid":858194,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:40:35.000Z","msg":"等緊你帶頭"},{"pid":"e15ca0f55f9a970a61015704ddb1695d4cb100f7","tid":858194,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"103d8f65c4f3c4893db838765971fea0e9070e29","tid":858194,"uid":99662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:53:55.000Z","msg":"死亡"},{"pid":"565ce1b1cc58fe2d44374e5e6d8ac5ce7abc8e0e","tid":858194,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T19:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2617cca82a02b197c3b4b50c1feb46e42f952c","tid":858194,"uid":11081,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1f1e9